  <!-- ORIGINAL
  Sturdy pieces of wood lashed together with leather or fabric for storing large quantities of weaponry. Does not prevent deterioration. Prevents weaponry from affecting the beauty of its surroundings. 

  Total Capacity: 8 Stacks -->
